<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693586>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 146. Distribution map of Copestylum bulbosum (Fluke, 1951) (red circles); Copestylum bolivianum (Hine, 1914) (yellow circles); Copestylum bradleyi (Curran, 1925) (blue circles); Copestylum cockerelli (Curran, 1927) (black circles); Copestylum peruvianum (Vimmer & Soukup, 1839) (green circles); Copestylum parina (Fluke, 1951) (pink circles); Copestylum smithae (Thompson, 1965) (black triangles) in Chile." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4693586/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693570>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 118–121. Copestylum smithae (Thompson, 1965): (118) lateral view and (119) dorsal view. Scale bars = 1.5 mm (photos by Vicente Valdés). Copestylum azurea (Philippi, 1865): (120) lateral view (Photo by Vicente Valdés). Scale bar = 2 mm, and (121) dorsal view (photo by Matías Barceló). Scale bar = 3 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4693570/files/figure.png" .

